                <view class="weui-media-box__desc">由各种物质组成的巨型球状天体，叫做星球。星球有一定的形状，有自己的运行轨道。</view>
                <view class="weui-media-box__info">
                    <view class="weui-media-box__info__meta">已交/未交：未登记</view>
                    <view class="weui-media-box__info__meta">已批/未批：未批改</view>
                    <view class="weui-media-box__info__meta">平均分：60分</view>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="weui-panel">
        <view class="weui-panel__hd">语文作业【一年级 1603班】| 2008-01-01</view>
        <view class="weui-panel__bd">
            <view class="weui-media-box weui-media-box_text">
                <view class="weui-media-box__desc">由各种物质组成的巨型球状天体，叫做星球。星球有一定的形状，有自己的运行轨道。</view>
                <view class="weui-media-box__info">
                    <view class="weui-media-box__info__meta">已交/未交：未登记</view>
                    <view class="weui-media-box__info__meta">已批/未批：未批改</view>
